						               													<description>Safe City - Another Road is an educational card game.&amp;#10;Make your city's road infrastructure more friendly and practical. Discover safe solutions for traffic walking and cycling, as well as car and public transport. Create your own set of road safety solutions. Compete with other players by creating the right connections and dependencies and score as many security points as possible. May the safest city win!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Safe City - Another Road is a tableau building card game for 2 to 4 players aging 10 and up, taking around 15 minutes to play. Players draft cards, then, each player places the chosen card in his set in the corresponding column next to the main color card.&amp;#10;If the card has an instant effect it&amp;rsquo;s resolver immediately, but most will have effect only during the final scoring.&amp;#10;After all cards are placed in sets the game ends and scoring begins. Each player in turn analyses each card from the set. The player with the most VP wins the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
